== 起源 ==
海王星最大的衛星[[海衛一|崔頓]]是一顆軌道[[順行和逆行|逆行]]，且大角度[[軌道傾角|傾斜]]的衛星。據推測，崔頓是在原始的海王星系統形成後，才被從[[古柏帶|古柏帶]]捕獲。先前存在的衛星會因為此一事件而改變軌道，導致一些衛星彈射出去或和其它的衛星碰撞而被破壞<ref name="Goldreich1989">{{cite journal|last=Goldreich|first=P.|last2=Murray|first2=N. |last3=Longaretti |first3=P. Y. |last4= Banfield |first4= D. |title=Neptune's story|journal=Science|volume=245|date=1989|pages=500–504|bibcode=1989Sci...245..500G|doi=10.1126/science.245.4917.500|pmid=17750259|issue=4917}}</ref><ref name="Agnor06">{{cite journal
| last = Agnor
| first = C. B.| last2 = Hamilton| first2 = D. P.
| title = Neptune's capture of its moon Triton in a binary–planet gravitational encounter
| journal = Nature | date = 2006-05-11
| volume = 441 | issue = 7090 | pages = 192–194
| doi = 10.1038/nature04792 | pmid = 16688170 | bibcode = 2006Natur.441..192A}}</ref>。 至少，現在存在的海王星內側衛星是在崔頓的軌道受到[[潮汐加速|潮汐減速]]之後，從碎石的廢墟中[[吸積|吸積]]形成的<ref name="BanfieldMurray">{{cite journal| doi = 10.1016/0019-1035(92)90155-Z| last1 = Banfield| first1 = Don| last2 = Murray| first2 = Norm| date=October 1992 | title = A dynamical history of the inner Neptunian satellites| journal = Icarus| volume = 99| issue = 2| pages = 390–401| pmid = | pmc = | bibcode = 1992Icar...99..390B| ref = harv}}</ref>。

另一個假設認為，希波坎普可能是從最靠近海王星的大衛星，[[海衛八|普羅杜斯]]（海衛八）受到撞擊產生的碎屑形成的<ref name="KarlHille" /><ref name="Showalter2019">{{cite journal|last1= Showalter|first1=M. R.|last2=de Pater|first2= I.|last3= Lissauer|first3=J. J.|last4= French|first4=R. S.|title= The seventh inner moon of Neptune|journal= Nature|volume= 566|issue= 7744|year= 2019|pages= 350–353|doi= 10.1038/s41586-019-0909-9}}</ref>。碎屑可能是由彗星撞擊的最大隕石坑[[海衛八#表面特徵|法羅斯撞擊坑]]噴出的；由這個撞擊坑噴出的物質，體積大約是希波坎普的50倍。希波坎普的軌道相對地靠近普羅杜斯，它們的[[半長軸|半長軸]]相差約12,000公里。希波坎普可能在距離普羅杜斯只有數千公里之內形成，然後由於它與海王星相互的潮汐作用更為強烈，才與普羅杜斯拉開了距離<ref name="Showalter2019" />。

== 物理性質 ==
[[File:Neptune_and_its_smallest_moon_Hippocamp_(artist’s_impression).jpg|left]]

一般認為希波坎普的表面類似其它的內側衛星一樣，像"骯髒的瀝青"一樣黑  <ref name = "Showalter_blog" />。它們的幾何[[反照率|反照率]]範圍在0.07至0.10之間 <ref name=Karkoschka2003>{{cite journal| doi = 10.1016/S0019-1035(03)00002-2| last = Karkoschka| first = Erich| year = 2003| title = Sizes, shapes, and albedos of the inner satellites of Neptune| journal = Icarus| volume = 162| issue = 2| pages = 400–407| bibcode = 2003Icar..162..400K| ref = harv}}</ref>。最初，依據希波坎普26.5的[[視星等|視星等]]估計，它的直徑在16至20公里，使它成為海王星最小的衛星。最近對海王星衛星的觀測顯示，希波坎普的直徑為34.8公里，幾乎是先前估計的兩倍<ref name="Showalter2019"/>。然而，它依然是海王星內側，常規衛星中最小的。

使用哈伯太空望遠鏡的[[近紅外線照相機和多目標分光儀|近紅外線照相機和多目標分光儀]]（NICMOS）檢查了海王星環和內側衛星的{{link-en|近紅外光譜|Near-infrared spectroscopy}}<ref name="DumasTerrile2002">{{cite journal|last1=Dumas|first1=C.|last2=Terrile|first2=R. J.|last3=Smith|first3=B. A.|last4=Schneider|first4=G.|title=Astrometry and Near-Infrared Photometry of Neptune's Inner Satellites and Ring Arcs|journal=The Astronomical Journal|volume=123|issue=3|date= March 2002|pages=1776–1783|issn= 0004-6256|doi=10.1086/339022|bibcode = 2002AJ....123.1776D }}</ref><ref name="DumasSmith2003"/>，類似[[太陽系小天體|太陽系小天體]][[托林_(天文學)|黑暗、紅化物質]]的特徵，似乎存在於其所有的表面。資料顯示含有有機化合物[[碳-氫鍵|碳-氫鍵]]（C-H鍵）、和/或[[碳－氮鍵|碳－氮鍵]]（C≡N）的結合<ref name="DumasSmith2003">{{cite journal|last1=Dumas|first1=C.|last2=Smith|first2=B. A.|last3=Terrile|first3=R. J.|title=Hubble Space Telescope NICMOS Multiband Photometry of Proteus and Puck|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomical-journal_2003-08_126_2/page/1080|journal=The Astronomical Journal|volume= 126|issue=2|date= August 2003|pages= 1080–1085|issn=0004-6256|doi=10.1086/375909|bibcode = 2003AJ....126.1080D }}</ref>，但光譜的解析度不足以識別是何種分子。認為存在外太陽系富含的水冰，但是在光譜中無法觀察到其特徵（不像[[天王星|天王星]]的小衛星）<ref name="DumasSmith2003"/>。

== 軌道屬性 ==
[[File:Orbits_of_inner_moons_of_Neptune_including_S_2004_N_1.jpg|thumb]]

希波坎普每22小時28.1分鐘（0.9362天）公轉海王星一圈<ref name = "Beatty_2013"/>，暗示它的軌道[[半長軸|半長軸]]，或軌道距離約為{{convert|105283|km|abbr=on}}，正好略高於[[月球#軌道|地月距離]]的四分之一，或大約是[[海王星環|海王星環]]平均半徑的兩倍。它的軌道傾角和離心率都接近零<ref name = "Beatty_2013"/>，並介於[[海衛七|拉里薩]]和[[海衛八|普羅杜斯]]之間，成為海王星外層[[規則衛星|規則衛星]]的第二顆。這種衛星的趨勢是直徑隨者與主體行星的距離增加而增加，但它卻反其道而行，是在這個位置上最小的衛星<ref name = "Sky&Tel_table">{{cite web | last = Editors of ''Sky & Telescope'' | title = A Guide to Planetary Satellites | work = ''Sky & Telescope'' web site | publisher = [[Sky_&_Telescope|Sky & Telescope]] | url = http://www.skyandtelescope.com/observing/objects/planets/A_Guide_to_Planetary_Satellites.html?page=4 | accessdate = 2013-07-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131016023130/http://www.skyandtelescope.com/observing/objects/planets/A_Guide_to_Planetary_Satellites.html?page=4 | archive-date = 2013-10-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

拉里薩和西坡坎普的週期有著3:5的[[軌道共振|軌道共振]]，差異只有1%左右；而希波坎普和普羅杜斯的週期有差異少於0.1%以內的5:6共振<ref group=Note>這三顆衛星的軌道週期各自為0.55465、0.93618和1.12231天，實際的比率值為2.962：5.000：5.994</ref>。一般認為拉里薩和普羅杜斯在幾億年前可能經歷了1:2的平均運動共振<ref name="ZhangHamilton2007">{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1=K.|last2=Hamilton|first2=D. P.|title=Orbital resonances in the inner neptunian system: I. The 2:1 Proteus–Larissa mean-motion resonance|journal=Icarus|volume= 188|issue=2|date=June 2007|pages= 386–399|issn= 0019-1035|doi= 10.1016/j.icarus.2006.12.002|bibcode = 2007Icar..188..386Z }}</ref><ref name="ZhangHamilton2008">{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1= K.|last2=Hamilton|first2=D. P.|title=Orbital resonances in the inner neptunian system: II. Resonant history of Proteus, Larissa, Galatea, and Despina|journal=Icarus|volume= 193|issue=1|date= January 2008|pages=267–282|issn= 0019-1035|doi= 10.1016/j.icarus.2007.08.024|bibcode = 2008Icar..193..267Z }}</ref>。普羅杜斯<ref name="ZhangHamilton2007"/>和希波坎普因為在海王星的[[同步軌道|同步軌道]]之外（海王星的自轉週期為0.6713天<ref name="fact">{{cite web |last = Williams |first = David R. |date = 1 September 2004 |url = http://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/factsheet/neptunefact.html |title = Neptune Fact Sheet |publisher = [[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate = 18 July 2013 |archive-date = 2011-08-17 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/610c2BTlB?url=http://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/factsheet/neptunefact.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>)，所以一直在遠離拉里薩，並因此被[[潮汐加速|潮汐加速]]，而拉里薩在其內，則受到潮汐減速<ref name="ZhangHamilton2007"/>。

== 命名 ==
這顆衛星以[[希臘神話|希臘神話]]中的生物，[[馬頭魚尾怪|馬頭魚尾怪]]（Hippocamp）命名為希波坎普<ref>{{cite web |last1=Timmer |first1=John |title=Hubble images show a Neptune moon that may have been repeatedly reborn |url=https://arstechnica.com/science/2019/02/researchers-develop-a-technique-that-spots-tiny-moon-orbiting-neptune/ |website=Ars Technica |accessdate=21 February 2019 |language=en-us |date=20 February 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107223734/https://arstechnica.com/science/2019/02/researchers-develop-a-technique-that-spots-tiny-moon-orbiting-neptune/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這顆衛星在2013年編號為海衛十四，但直到2019年2月才獲得正式的名字。

發現小組決定依據[[古希臘羅馬神話|古希臘羅馬神話]]中與海神[[波塞冬|波塞冬]]或[[尼普頓|尼普頓]]有關的一張圖中，向[[國際天文學聯合會|國際天文學聯合會]]提交<ref name = "Klotz_2013"/>與海王星其它[[海王星的衛星|衛星]]一致的名稱<ref name="Gazetteer">{{Cite web|title=Planet and Satellite Names and Discoverers|work=Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature|publisher=USGS Astrogeology|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/append7.html|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-date=2009-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091010085334/http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/append7.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 考慮的名稱包括波塞冬獨眼的大兒子[[波利菲莫斯|波利菲莫斯]]（Polyphemus）和[[托俄薩|托俄薩]]（Thoosa）<ref>{{cite news|last=Vincent|first=James|title=Astronomers throw open the doors to the public-naming of planets|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/astronomers-throw-open-the-doors-to-the-publicnaming-of-planets-8770592.html|accessdate=16 August 2013|newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=16 August 2013|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925152814/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/astronomers-throw-open-the-doors-to-the-publicnaming-of-planets-8770592.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。團隊的領導人，肖華特選擇了西坡坎普這個名字，部分原因是認同"海馬屬"的[[海馬|海馬]]恰如其分的有著馬頭魚尾<ref name="TheGuardian">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2019/feb/20/scientists-build-picture-of-super-fast-mini-moon-of-neptune/ |title='Breakneck speed' mini moon hurtles around Neptune at 20,000mph |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |author=Ian Sample |date=2019-02-20 |accessdate=2019-02-20 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113091821/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2019/feb/20/scientists-build-picture-of-super-fast-mini-moon-of-neptune |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2019年，國際天文學聯合會接受了希波坎普的名字<ref name="Mortillaro">{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/neptune-moon-hippocamp-1.5025091 |date=20 February 2019 |title=Scientists reveal Neptune's tiny new moon, Hippocamp |accessdate=20 February 2019 |first=Nicole |last=Mortillaro   |work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |archive-date=2020-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213073928/https://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/neptune-moon-hippocamp-1.5025091 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

